msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.5.2"
msgid "“Na mayaṃ paṇḍitā byattā medhāvī bahussutā dhammakathikā, natthamhākaṃ duggati, sugatiyeva amhākaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā”ti bhaṇati."
msgstr "“We’re not wise ones/we’re not competent ones/we’re not intelligent ones/we’re not learned ones/we’re not expounders of the Teaching/we’re not going to a bad destination/we can only expect a good destination,”"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.5.3"
msgid "Āpatti vācāya, vācāya dukkaṭassa."
msgstr "then for every statement, he commits an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.6.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Abuse of one who is not fully ordained"

