msgid "Upasampanno anupasampannaṃ khuṃsetukāmo vambhetukāmo maṅkukattukāmo evaṃ vadeti, “santi idhekacce caṇḍālā venā nesādā rathakārā pukkusā”ti bhaṇati … pe …."
msgstr "If one who is fully ordained, wishing to revile, wishing to insult, wishing to humiliate someone who is not fully ordained, says this, “There are outcasts/bamboo workers/hunters/chariot-makers/waste-removers, right here” …"

