msgstr "If one who is fully ordained, not wishing to revile, not wishing to insult, not wishing to humiliate another who is fully ordained, but wanting to have fun, says what is high to one who is high—an aristocrat/a brahmin—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.7.8"
msgid "“khattiyosi, brāhmaṇosī”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, vācāya dubbhāsitassa."
msgstr "saying, “You’re an aristocrat/you’re a brahmin,” then for every statement, he commits an offense of bad speech."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="73"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa101"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.7.9"
msgid "Upasampanno upasampannaṃ na khuṃsetukāmo na vambhetukāmo na maṅkukattukāmo, davakamyatā hīnena hīnaṃ vadeti … pe …"
msgstr "If one who is fully ordained, not wishing to revile, not wishing to insult, not wishing to humiliate another who is fully ordained, but wanting to have fun, says what is low to one who is low …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.7.10"
msgid "hīnena ukkaṭṭhaṃ vadeti … pe …"
msgstr "says what is low to one who is high …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.7.11"
msgid "ukkaṭṭhena hīnaṃ vadeti … pe …"
msgstr "says what is high to one who is low …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.7.12"
msgid "ukkaṭṭhena ukkaṭṭhaṃ vadeti, paṇḍitaṃ byattaṃ medhāviṃ bahussutaṃ dhammakathikaṃ—"
msgstr "says what is high to one who is high—one who is wise/one who is competent/one who is intelligent/one who is learned/one who is an expounder of the Teaching—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.7.13"
msgid "“paṇḍitosi, byattosi, medhāvīsi, bahussutosi, dhammakathikosi, natthi tuyhaṃ duggati, sugatiyeva tuyhaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, vācāya dubbhāsitassa."
msgstr "saying, “You’re wise/you’re competent/you’re intelligent/you’re learned/you’re an expounder of the Teaching/you’re not going to a bad destination/you can only expect a good destination,” then for every statement, he commits an offense of bad speech."

#. </p><h5>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.7.13a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Not intending to abuse, indirect speech"

#. </h5><p><a class="sc" id="74"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="wt-pa102"></a> 
