msgstr "If one who is fully ordained, not wishing to revile, not wishing to insult, not wishing to humiliate someone who is not fully ordained, but wanting to have fun, says what is low to one who is low …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.8.2"
msgid "hīnena ukkaṭṭhaṃ vadeti … pe …"
msgstr "says what is low to one who is high …"

