msgstr "If one who is fully ordained, not wishing to revile, not wishing to insult, not wishing to humiliate someone who is not fully ordained, but wanting to have fun, says this, “There are outcasts/bamboo workers/hunters/chariot-makers/waste-removers, right here” …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-pc2:pts-cs2.8.7"
msgid "“Santi idhekacce paṇḍitā byattā medhāvī bahussutā dhammakathikā, natthi tesaṃ duggati, sugatiyeva tesaṃ pāṭikaṅkhā”ti bhaṇati, āpatti vācāya, vācāya dubbhāsitassa."
